{"relevantArticles":[{"articleTitle":"证道歌","articleAbstractText":"《证道歌》是唐代高僧永嘉玄觉禅师悟道后心得精华的文字记录。这首诗歌凝聚了佛教智慧和人生智慧的特有风采，产生了较为深远的影响。全诗二百四十七句，为长篇杂言形式，语言文字通俗，阐扬佛学禅理，唐宋时广为流传。","articleStatus":0,"articlePermalink":"/articles/2021/01/24/1611492658816.html","articleImg1URL":"https://b3logfile.com/bing/20190221.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1280/h/720/interlace/1/q/100"},{"articleTitle":"金刚萨埵百字明","articleAbstractText":"\u201c金刚萨埵\u201d，亦作\u201c金刚萨垛\u201d(藏传佛教密宗）。金刚萨埵百字明咒，又作金刚萨埵咒、百字真言、百字明、金刚萨埵百字明等。","articleStatus":0,"articlePermalink":"/articles/2021/01/24/1611491064594.html","articleImg1URL":"https://b3logfile.com/bing/20181027.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1280/h/720/interlace/1/q/100"},{"articleTitle":"金刚般若波罗蜜经","articleAbstractText":"无上甚深微妙法 百千万劫难遭遇 我今见闻得受持 愿解如来真实义","articleStatus":0,"articlePermalink":"/articles/2021/01/23/1611396693126.html","articleImg1URL":"https://b3logfile.com/bing/20190619.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1280/h/720/interlace/1/q/100"},{"articleTitle":"楞严咒全文","articleAbstractText":"楞严咒又名大方广妙莲华王十方佛母陀罗尼咒、佛顶神咒。","articleStatus":0,"articlePermalink":"/articles/2021/01/21/1611243412613.html","articleImg1URL":"https://b3logfile.com/bing/20200424.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1280/h/720/interlace/1/q/100"}]}